tag name|||Cthulhu: Books of Ancients VR
tag jj|||Cthulhu: Books of Ancients is a first-person horror game in which we take on the role of a detective looking for a missing six children. A mysterious note thrown by an unknown informant at the door led him to the library of the University of Miskatonic, where there are clues to solve the puzzle.  Main game features: Detective case to be solved The secrets of the Ancients Ones Ancient rituals Summon and recall demons Magic items inspired by Cthulhu Mythology Miskatonic Library in Arkham Innsmouth Herald Newspaper Necronomicon and the books of the Ancient Ones
